title: Artistry vs Technical - what's more important in figure skating?
description: We spoke to 2020 U.S. National silver medallist Mariah Bell, Olympic medallist Adam Rippon, Olympic champion Meryl Davis, and figure skating expert Jackie Wong to find their views on a question that has dominated the sport for decades.
